# .dev.vars.example — template for local Cloudflare Worker vars
#
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (which is gitignored) and fill with LOCAL values only.
# NEVER put real production secrets here or commit a populated .dev.vars.
#
# Step 2: the Worker proxies read-only GETs to ORIGIN_URL. The deployed default
# (https://djzs.ai) lives in wrangler.toml [vars]. Override it here to test the
# proxy against a LOCAL Express instance instead of hitting production:
#
# ORIGIN_URL=http://localhost:5000
#
# BINDINGS: TBD
# No secrets/bindings are used by the Worker yet. When that changes (later, approved
# step), document the LOCAL placeholder values here, e.g.:
# DJZS_TRUST_TOKEN=replac...n
